overloads.summary:
Generates a conversion from the source type to the intermediate type. This override
            will convert a string value to <see cref="T:System.DateTime" />, <see cref="T:System.DateTimeOffset" />,
            <see cref="T:System.Guid" />, <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" />, or <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> prior to applying
            the base implementation.
